body:
Well , today I tried to check how many hours I have played in ' League of Legends.' But what put me in Utterly shock was a message displayed on my screen that stated -- '' Due RIOT policy, developers are no longer able to retrieve non ranked games because of : "Any reason why normal games are now considered private information ? Normal games have always been considered private information." 

FeelsBadMan ; Hopefully Riot can figure out a way so we are still able to see our total hours of gameplay. 

Any thoughts on this? :^) {{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}
